Text: Goals ObjectivesForwarded by Beth A RyanHOUECT on PM Brian Redmond PM To cc Subject Goals Objectives Team The attached provides a summary of our goals objectives for We have a number of challenges this year but we making good progress building on our success in The goals and objectives were developed as part of last years budget process and were refined during our recent offsite A compilation of the presentations from the offsite were distributed to each of the VPs for discussion with their groups It will take continued effort from each of us to shift our source of earnings from monetizations to commercial origination As always your ideas and active participation is encouraged Regards Brian
